Packages 
Package Description
com.proteusframework.ui
UI configurations.
net.proteusframework.data.filesystem
UI classes for filesystem API.
net.proteusframework.ui.mcolumn
Column based table / tree API.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt
MIWT is a web toolkit for rapidly building user interfaces.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component
This package is for primitive components.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.composite
This package is for composite components which are components that are built from other components.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.composite.editor
Classes to help implement property editor patterns.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.event
Events specific to components live here.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data
Data models for components live here.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data.event
Events specific to data models live here.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.dnd
Drag and drop API.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.event
Events not specific to another package and classes that manage events live here.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.external
Supports operations outside of the MIWT environment, such as saving resources to disk, opening an URL, etc.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.input
Defines a generic input system that a medium implementation may use.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.layout
Use of layout API is deprecated.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.locale
Provides an internationalization framework for MIWT.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.locale.impl
This package provides the implementation for TranslatorApplication.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.resource
MIWT resources.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.util
Classes in this package provide some helper methods.
net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.validation
This package contains classes related to component validation.
net.proteusframework.ui.search
Classes for modeling search criteria, results, and UI needs.
net.proteusframework.ui.workspace
The workspace API provides a framework for managing UIs based on tasks and events.
